Class RomanNumeral

java.lang.Object
RomanNumeral
public class RomanNumeral extends Object
A class that calculates and records the Roman numerals and their converted Arabic values. It also provides toString, equals, and compareTo methods for RomanNumeral objects
Author:
Anthony Jerez
